<div id="review_3836138531" class="review nosyndicate" itemprop="reviews" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Review">
  <link itemprop="url" href="https://www.goodreads.com/review/show/3836138531" />
    <a title="Angie Dutton" class="left imgcol" href="/user/show/130172564-angie-dutton"><img alt="Angie Dutton" src="https://images.gr-assets.com/users/1613060904p2/130172564.jpg" /></a>

  <div class="left bodycol">
    <div class="reviewHeader uitext stacked">
        <a class="reviewDate createdAt right" href="/review/show/3836138531?book_show_action=true">Jun 07, 2021</a>

      <span itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Person">
        <a title="Angie Dutton" class="user" itemprop="url" name="Angie Dutton" href="/user/show/130172564-angie-dutton">Angie Dutton</a>
      </span>

        rated it
        <span class=" staticStars notranslate" title="it was amazing"><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10">it was amazing</span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span></span>



        

    </div>


        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer3836138531" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer6640242171809227799">I made a promise to myself not to read two Dick books in a row, simply because I&apos;d end up reading nothing but Dick. But this is definitely worth reading straight after Radio Free... even if it repeats the same information it does so in a way that actually expands the concepts further. </span>
  <span id="freeText6640242171809227799" style="display:none">I made a promise to myself not to read two Dick books in a row, simply because I'd end up reading nothing but Dick. But this is definitely worth reading straight after Radio Free... even if it repeats the same information it does so in a way that actually expands the concepts further. </span>
  <a data-text-id="6640242171809227799" href="#" onclick="swapContent($(this));; return false;">...more</a>

          </span>
        </div>


      <div class="reviewFooter uitext buttons">
          

